  "text": "RT-PCR was performed with RT-PCR High-plus-(Toyobo, Osaka, Japan) using gene-specific primers designed to target Actin2, MPK3, MPK4, WRKY6, and NPR1. The gene-specific primers for RT-PCR analysis were used as described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
